{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"b0a53064-6f90-4f30-adae-a4a8d6a04dca","content":"There's no workflow file in this directory, so here's a general guide. The key changes are:\n\n### 1. Add OIDC permissions to your job\n\n```yaml\npermissions:\n  id-token: write   # Required for OIDC token request\n  contents: read\n```\n\n### 2. Replace `dotnet nuget push` with the trusted-publishing action\n\n**Before:**\n```yaml\n- run: dotnet nuget push **/*.nupkg\n    --api-key ${{ secrets.NUGET_API_KEY }}\n    --source https://api.nuget.org/v3/index.json\n```\n\n**After:**\n```yaml\n- uses: dotnet/publish-nuget-action@v1\n  with:\n    nuget-source: https://api.nuget.org/v3/index.json\n    nupkg-path: '**/*.nupkg'\n```\n\nNo API key needed — the action exchanges a GitHub OIDC token for a short-lived NuGet publish token.\n\n### 3. Register your repo on nuget.org\n\nGo to **nuget.org → Manage Packages → Trusted Publishers** and add your GitHub repository (owner, repo, workflow file, and optionally the environment name).\n\n### 4. (Optional but recommended) Use a GitHub environment\n\n```yaml\njobs:\n  publish:\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    environment: nuget-publish   # ties to environment-scoped trust policy\n    permissions:\n      id-token: write\n      contents: read\n```\n\nThis scopes the OIDC trust to a specific environment, adding an approval gate if desired.\n\n### Summary of what to remove\n- Delete `secrets.NUGET_API_KEY` from your repo/org secrets (after verifying the new flow works).\n- Remove any `--api-key` flags from `dotnet nuget push` commands.\n\nWould you like me to modify a specific workflow file?","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"188cc331-f190-44a5-adc2-d093f638caac","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The directory appears to be empty. The user is asking a general question about switching from NuGet API key to trusted publishing (OIDC) in GitHub Actions. There's no actual workflow file to modify. Let me provide guidance based on my knowledge.","outputTokens":519},"id":"81fd47ab-d81c-440a-83dd-9f10e0c6dce7","timestamp":"2026-04-03T00:41:33.463Z","parentId":"2edeeb29-d771-472a-8acf-9deb976bef6b"}
